        "text": "=ðŸ”§ **Critical Configuration Change Detected**\n\n**Event ID:** {{ $json.event_id }}\n**Device:** {{ $json.device_name }}\n**Section:** {{ $json.config_section }}\n**Change Type:** {{ $json.change_type }}\n**User:** {{ $json.user }}\n**Time:** {{ $json.timestamp }}\n\n**Details:**\n```\n{{ $json.message }}\n```\n\nâš ï¸ *This change requires review*",
